## Installing the Chart

### Add Helm Repository

```bash
helm repo add {{ template "custom.helm.name" . }} {{ template "custom.helm.url" . }}
helm repo update
```

### Install Chart

To install the chart with the release name `my-{{ .Name }}`:

```bash
helm install my-{{ .Name }} {{ template "custom.helm.name" . }}/{{ .Name }}
```

### Install with Custom Values

```bash
helm install my-{{ .Name }} {{ template "custom.helm.name" . }}/{{ .Name }} -f values.yaml
```

### Install in Specific Namespace

```bash
helm install my-{{ .Name }} {{ template "custom.helm.name" . }}/{{ .Name }} -n my-namespace --create-namespace
```
{{- end -}}

